replication controller ek pod ho ya dher sare sabko watch krta hai agr pod unheathy hua to nya create krwayega.
replication controller load ko balance krta aur scale krta hai
replica set sab replication ctroller wala sab kaam krr leta hai but vo upgraded version hai aur vo nye pod ko bhi manage krta hai jo replica set k under nh bna.
replicaset also monitor the pods.
labels under selector help krta hai replica set ko pta lagane me kaunse pods ko hume manage krna hai.
hume replica set ka number increase krna hoto hum kaise krenge usk liye many ways jaise yml file update kro aur "kubectl replace -f filename" command chla do .
second way "kubectl scale --replicas=6 -f file name"
